Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: This happened\Nwhile we were gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Friendship quests\Nbeyond Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: We're\Ngonna open a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighsay: We expect you to\Ndo things by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: We have a huge\Nresponsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I need you all to\Ndo this by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These ponies are the\Nheroes of Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus: This is just a quick\Nmental health break!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighsay: The school\Nis under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are students!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am shutting\Nthis school DOWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You feeling OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure the EEA closed\Nyour Friendship School,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you've got\Ntime to do other stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like being on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A failure vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be the\NPrincess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And all I did was make enemies\Nwith Equestria's allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,upset my friends,\Nand get my school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,unaccredited!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE IS NO BRIGHT SIDE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,OK then. I'm gonna\Nneed backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Cheer Up is a go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sit around in\Nthe boring dark all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What you need is a double dose\Nof Granny Smith's apple mash.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm sad, a\Nhug from Angel Bunny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,always makes me\Nfeel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Maybe it's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I find that nothing brightens\Nmy mood like a new ensemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Thanks, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing] for somepony who\Nknows how to run a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't tell me\Nthis was a pity party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've brought ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you trying\Nto make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But not everything can\Nbe fixed with dresses and cupcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:02:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need some time\Nto be alone and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered how\Nlong you'd take
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to get tired of\Npillow fort pouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony's already\Ntried to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna\Ncheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tell you\Nwhat you did wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave up too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you made me a\Nguidance counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That means tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighsay was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The school WAS a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So was I when\Nyou met me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you showed me that\Nwhen you know in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,something is right,\Nyou stand up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go against the EEA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in charge of all of\Nthe schools in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in charge of all\Nthe Friendship in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you\Nlet somepony else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,stop you from\Ndoing your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But the EEA rule book--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[splash]\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can write\Nyour own rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're doing\Nsomething new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY we're doing this\Nis way more important
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,than HOW we're\Ndoing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we ARE\Ndoing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's the\NTwilight I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[door opens] Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The School of Friendship\Nis back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we still get\Nto guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, Twilight, but\Nteaching at that school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was the most boring,\Nhorrible, awful thing ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Pretty sure she's gonna\Ntake offense to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Rainbow Dash\Nis right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you all an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so focused on\Ndoing things the EEA way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't listen to\Nany of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I\Npromise this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll run the school\Nlike friends should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'd be allowed to\Nteach however we want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No more scary\Npop quizzes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Confetti cannons\Nfor every creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you need to teach\Nthe elements of harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippppeeeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case, we're\Nbehind you 100%, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Ahem, just\Ntwo small problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The school is still\Nunaccredited...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have\Nany students.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of\Nthe first part,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if you five can\Nround up our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Roundin' up the pony students\Nain't gonna be an issue but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The creatures from\Nthe other kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed pretty\Nupset with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft. Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain we can win them\Nover with our charm and style!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcake gram for\NPrince Rutherford!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Pink Pony here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks mad at ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Beeee-cause you don't\Nhave to be mad anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reopening Twilight\NSparkle's School of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's gonna be super-\Nooper-dooper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,better than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ever so sorry about\Nthe misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All creatures are\Nof course welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be really happy\Nif you sent your student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be the\Nsame without 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're open and ready\Nto start teaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What are you\Nwaiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your student\Nand let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, do you need me to\Ndo the whole apology
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and explanation thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not happening\Nbecause--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUR STUDENT IS GONE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Rutherford: WHERE YONA!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This all Ponies' fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty quick\Nto blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Nhiding, Yak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, can we just focus on\Nfinding our lost students?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You grubs are probably\Nhiding the whole lot of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, everycreature, if\Nyou can just explain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The students left us notes\Nbefore they disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When the school closed, they\Ndidn't want to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They claim they ran\Naway to stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They did learn friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The students couldn't have\Ndone this by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,SOME creature is hiding them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If the niece of our\Nqueen is not found soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise there\Nwill be retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Well, my dragons\Nwill burn every kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,until we find which of\Nyou is hiding Smolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell it to the Griffon Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaks fight griffons\Nand dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Changeling\NEmpire can't afford
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,an international incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If any creature blames the\NChangelings for this--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up\Nto, shape-shifter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the students\Nquickly, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I fear our world\Nwill be at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: OK. Let's\Nreview what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder, Ocellus,\NSilverstream, Yona,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and Gallus\Ndisappeared together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably just\Noff hidin' somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless they used some kind\Nof spell to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Or went undercover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were attacked\Nby a ferocious shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony EVER expects that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Shrimps can attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. That's why\Nnopony expects it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm just, uh...\Nreally hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to think\Nlike our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone told us we would\Nnever see each other again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what would we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go someplace we\Ncould all hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat lots and\Nlots of cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What..?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar was friends with\Nall of the missing students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And he just got\Nplenty of cupcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... He was at the\Nfarm this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,picking up a\Nwagonload of apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw him in a shop\Nbuying pillows and blankets!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] He must be\Ntaking all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to the other students!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. This place is way cooler\Nthan I thought it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even{\i1} I'm{\i0} impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called\Nagain, Ocellus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Castle of the\NTwo Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered it from class:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight's History of\NPre-Equestrian Friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,School was actually\Ngood for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not really like school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona like new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Smolder...Like...Breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream: Hey, you\Nguys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes are best cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Thanks for the\Nassist, Gallus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff. I was saving the cupcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pillows, how nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle is going to\Nbe so much more comfy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pillow fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Silverstream: YOU GUYS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,STAIRS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And ... we care because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stairs are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anything\Nlike 'em underwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way to climb 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If only my family back\Nhome could see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the other Changelings\Ncould meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not nearly as\Nstrange as the stories say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, hanging out\Nwith other creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually...not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, MOST other creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is THAT thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Am I the ONLY one who\Ndidn't sleep through
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fluttershy's Critters\Nof Comfort and Conflict Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a puckwudgie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can make\Nfriends with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak plan better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,YAAAA!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Think, Ocellus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Professor Fluttershy\Nsay anything about
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,how to beat Puckwudgies\Nin her lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I'm sorry, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go ahead and\Nguess it's not pillows,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,apples...... or cupcakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't class have been about\Nhow to make friends with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, guys? They're\Ngetting really close...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Professor Egghead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Don't hurt them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask them to leave nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For pony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. They're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea our teachers\Nwere actually cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash was like zooooom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then whoooaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Puckwudgies went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the birds came and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We all\Njust lived it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty amazing...\Neven by dragon standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everycreature all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky we\Ngot here in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this probably\Nisn't the safest place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for a campout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're going\Nto send us back to our homes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have another\Noption in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty clear you've\Nalready started learning
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,friendship without\Nyour teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'd like to show\Nyou even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if you come back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we felt\Nexactly the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when Twilight told us she\Nwas reopening the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, we guarantee\Nit shall be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. With\Nclass run my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be TWO HUNDRED and\Ntwenty percent cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And without the EEA,\Nit'll be much friendlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus all your nations\Nwon't go to war
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if you come back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia: Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so relieved\Nto get your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As was Queen Novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're just glad you're\Nall right, Silverstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect a welcome\Nparty from me, sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time you got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This pony joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We're going\Nback to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How? You can't\Neven get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,School is back in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dared remove my seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did, Chancellor Neighsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I respectfully\Nask you to step aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or classes will start late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Classes won't start at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA has spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And NONE SHALL PASS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yak pass if Yak say! HMPH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The school was disorganized!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachers unqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And those dangerous and\Nunpredictable "students"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,put ponies' lives in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr! I'll show you unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Princess Twilight\NSparkle has a good explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that my\NSchool of Friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is EEA unaccredited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! She said it without\Ndoing the eye thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it is not a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an EEA school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a friendship school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,With its own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These students reminded me\Nthat every friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way we teach it\Nhas to be just as unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My school is going to\Ndo things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Allowing all of\Nthese creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to attend your school...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,changing the rules for them!\NIt simply won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to recall something\Nabout Earth Ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Unicorns and Pegasi doing\Nsomething similar, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you, Chancellor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,my school will help\Nprotect Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. How's this school gonna be\Nany different from last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ This brand new{\i0}\N{\i1} School of Friendship ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Is home to everyone ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're learning how to trust.♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're here to all have fun ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ With friendship{\i0}\N{\i1} ties that bind us ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Tighter than the{\i0}\N{\i1} strongest bonds ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We're hoof-in-hoof ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ In hand-in-hoof in{\i0}\N{\i1} wing or even... claw! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ There's a griffon{\i0}\N{\i1} in the garden ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Hippogriffs hang in the hall♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And the door will be open to{\i0}\N{\i1} all creatures great and small ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And a yak or two or three ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Sing in perfect harmony ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ That might have been a{\i0}\N{\i1} Changeling... ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ But it kinda looks like meeeeee ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The School of Friendship{\i0}\N{\i1} is for all of us ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A place where we belong ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Where we all learn{\i0}\N{\i1} to share and trust ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The only rule here is{\i0}\N{\i1} to find your way ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And friendship always wins{\i0}\N{\i1} at the end of the day ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Some things you just{\i0}\N{\i1} can't teach with books ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Some things you only know ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ So trust your heart{\i0}\N{\i1} and let us lead ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And your friendship's{\i0}\N{\i1} sure to grow. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And once we{\i0}\N{\i1} we master kindness ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We will spread it{\i0}\N{\i1} 'cross this land. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And give the gift{\i0}\N{\i1} that's ours to share ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ so others understand ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The School of Friendship{\i0}\N{\i1} is for all of us ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A place where we belong ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Where we all learn to{\i0}\N{\i1} share and trust ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The only rule here is{\i0}\N{\i1} to find your way ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And friendship always wins{\i0}\N{\i1} at the end of the day ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ember: Aw, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you promise to stop\Nsinging, Smolder can stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. If dragon stay, yak stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you will make the\NChangelings proud, Ocellus.
